nload NMCC Score Calculator (16K)</a><br>Don't sweat your score too much, just go out there and crush that AI!</p><h1>Play Hard and Enjoy!<br></h1><h2>To be in the rankings, submit three save files, 1AD, 1000AD and the game finish to <a href="mailto:anthonarz@rcn.com">anthonarz@rcn.com</a></h2><h3> Note : the saves don't have to be righton 1AD on 1000AD but try to remember to save as close to those dates as possible (and of coursedon't forget the finish).</h3></p><h2><p>Heres a list of past contestants : <a href="/fun/civ/rankings.html"><b>Previous Winners</a></p><br clear=all><img src="spacer.gif" width="1" height="9" alt=" "><br clear=all><img src="/Div.gif" width="100%" height="4" alt=""><br clear=all><img src="spacer.gif" width="1" height="9" alt=" "><br clear=all><p>Links back : </p><h2><a href="/fun/civilization.html"><b>Back to The Main Civ Seires Page</b></a></h2><h2><a href="/fun.html"><b>Back to The Fun Page</b></a></h2><a href="/index.html"><img src="/buttons/home.jpg" alt="Home" width="150" height="50" align="center"</a></body></html>